opennlp.ccg.synsem
Interface CategoryFcn

All Known Implementing Classes:
CategoryFcnAdapter
public interface CategoryFcn

A set of functions that can be applied to Categories. This is a way of getting around the fact that Java doesn't have 1st class functions. Thus, if a method is needed that takes a function that works on Categories, pass one of these instead.
